VIEWS to inspect priveleges:

USER_SYS_PRIVS    System privileges granted to the current user
USER_TAB_PRIVS    Grannted privileges on objects for which the use is the owner, grantor, or grantee
USER_ROLE_PRIVS   Roles ranted to the current user

DBA_SYS_PRIVS    System privileges granted to users and roles
DBA_TAB_PRIVS    All grants on objects in the DB
DPA_ROLE_PRIVS   Roles granted to users and roles

ROLE_SYS_PRIVS  System privileges granted to roles
ROLE_TAB_PRIVS  Table privileges granted to roles

SESSION_PRIVS    Session privileges that the user currently has set
